{"tid":57773,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有研究開小克D詞","createTime":"2016-12-28T09:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T12:54:49.000Z","uid":31215,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86f0be384f2a6240188fb3da2aa4c7aa49a57871","tid":57773,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:52:21.000Z","msg":"除左屈機的有時, 星塵, 重逢<br />\n仲有張繼聰生命之花<br />\n(New Age通識詞：生命之花--由多個圓圈組合而成的生命之花，象徵生命和宇宙的創造藍圖，是神聖幾何的一種。生命之花呈現的是果樹生命的周期，果樹生花、花變果實、果實藏種子，種子再長出果樹，生生不息，迴環往復。研究人員相信，觀察生命之花，等如揭開宇宙的智慧；亦有大量例證指出，遍佈世界各地的多個歷史遺蹟均不約而同地出現生命之花的圖像)<br />\n<br />\n知唔知仲有乜new age 詞?"},{"pid":"304507b9d2d64839d97a2f41cc20792b816b20b2","tid":57773,"uid":3152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"張氏情歌<br />\n玩字玩到出神入化<br />\n愛比死更冷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa9b3f4ebda056c0639eadf2ff7e3e01bd2199f","tid":57773,"uid":3152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張氏情歌<br />\n玩字玩到出神入化<br />\n愛比死更冷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNew age就唔知啦"},{"pid":"c865e9074c3cb5e43dd3e2a66b9762b90a45b98c","tid":57773,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:57:28.000Z","msg":"告別娑婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a5f7e254ef5729d84ff0ff9efee737ffa2ada7","tid":57773,"uid":14094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"主旋律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542ab853cb880b61152352fb394fb1ba7a9c63eb","tid":57773,"uid":10699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:11:20.000Z","msg":"有時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢仲要可以填返首有匙出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre