12%2F29%2F042026_6f79ee49fc475dca89275fc322fa6505.jpg&h=9724a297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個單元收錄咗佢＂被彈回頭＂作品，其中一首係畀許志安嘅半邊人，即出咗街嘅《心照不宣》，講到創作念頭構思佈局，亦有自已交唔出合格貨而決定退出嘅心路歴程，呢d都係得詞人自己先知嘅私事，佢肯寫係非常難得，亦好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393f5f91040ec52260d03f4823c3f073b6a49031","tid":57773,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T20:42:12.000Z","msg":"太長唔quote<br />\n本書叫廣東爆谷？見到就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9dacad8150af2e333828a2e845784b1e4caf87","tid":57773,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T20:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太長唔quote<br />\n本書叫廣東爆谷？見到就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三中商都有，有上下集，應該長期八折九折左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a047af26e6a8cb33c8c25f621ab92f9d6e002024","tid":57773,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T20:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>太長唔quote<br />\n本書叫廣東爆谷？見到就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三中商都有，有上下集，應該長期八折九折左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通巴打你就係小克？"},{"pid":"2f9199b1544113f9fb2f142cf147c0139e83d454","tid":57773,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T20:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>太長唔quote<br />\n本書叫廣東爆谷？見到就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三中商都有，有上下集，應該長期八折九折左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so